Class PlayerOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • propertytycoon.PlayerOption

  • public class PlayerOption
extends java.lang.Object
    The PlayerOption class represents one of the various options that the player if offered at each stage of the game. It contains a list of instructions that should be executed if the option is chosen
